---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Submit a Report">
  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Submit Your Experience</h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-8">
      Share your peptide experience to help others make informed decisions. All submissions are reviewed before publication.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-8 p-6 bg-white border border-border rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-3">What Makes a Good Report</h2>
      <ul class="text-muted space-y-2">
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Be specific:</strong> Include exact doses, timing, and duration</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Be honest:</strong> Include side effects, concerns, and things that didn't work</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Be detailed:</strong> Describe your timeline, what happened and when</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Include context:</strong> Age range, weight, relevant health conditions, concurrent medications</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Name your source:</strong> Compounding pharmacy, research supplier, international pharmacy, etc.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-3">Report Structure</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">Your report should cover:</p>
      <ol class="text-muted space-y-2 list-decimal list-inside">
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Background</strong>: Why you decided to try this peptide</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Protocol</strong>: Exactly what you did (dose, frequency, administration)</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Timeline</strong>: What happened over the course of use</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Side Effects</strong>: Everything you noticed, positive and negative</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Outcome</strong>: Your overall assessment and whether you'd do it again</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8 p-6 bg-accent/5 border border-accent/20 rounded-lg">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink mb-3">Submission Form</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">
        Fill out the form below. Your report will be reviewed and you'll be notified when it's published.
      </p>

      <iframe
        data-tally-src="https://tally.so/embed/dWaerN?alignLeft=1&hideTitle=1&transparentBackground=1"
        loading="lazy"
        width="100%"
        height="1200"
        frameborder="0"
        marginheight="0"
        marginwidth="0"
        title="Peptide Experience Report"
      ></iframe>
      <script src="https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js" async></script>
    </section>

    <section class="text-sm text-muted">
      <p class="mb-2">
        <strong class="text-ink">Privacy:</strong> Your email is only used to notify you of publication or ask follow-up questions. It's never published or shared.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong class="text-ink">Anonymity:</strong> Reports are published without identifying information unless you specifically request attribution.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
